        <h2 class="title">The issue.</h2>
        <p>Compared with other universities around the country, our voting rate is down. Not to mention that college students in general are one of the less well represented demographics, which compounds with issues of socio-economic status. According to the
            <a class="link" href="https://idhe.tufts.edu/nslve" target="_blank">National Study of Learning, Voting, and Education</a>, less than half of UVM's undergraduate students voted in the last general election.</p>

        <p class="bold">We can fix this.</p>
    </div>
</section>

