    <div class="inner-section mission">
        <h2 class="title">Our Solution</h2>
        <p>Through peer-to-peer contact over the course of three sessions between mid-September and election day, we'll increase voter turnout. This helps us break up the work of making sure people are registered, know where their polling place is (or have a mail-in ballot), and remember to turnout on election day.</p>
        <p>You can help out by getting involved!</p>
